,"next":{"title":"推理引擎概览","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/engine-overview"}},{"id":"03-gpu-basics/gpu-overview","title":"GPU 架构概览","description":"GPU 是 LLM 推理的唯一载体，理解其架构是性能优化的前提。","source":"@site/docs/03-gpu-basics/gpu-overview.md","sourceDirName":"03-gpu-basics","slug":"/03-gpu-basics/gpu-overview","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/gpu-overview","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":1,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":1},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"大模型微调实践","permalink":"/02-model-architecture/llm-finetuning"},"next":{"title":"GPU 显存模型","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/memory-model"}},{"id":"03-gpu-basics/memory-model","title":"GPU 显存模型","description":"LLM 推理的性能瓶颈不在算力，而在显存带宽。理解内存层级是优化的第一步。","source":"@site/docs/03-gpu-basics/memory-model.md","sourceDirName":"03-gpu-basics","slug":"/03-gpu-basics/memory-model","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/memory-model","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":2,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":2},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"GPU 架构概览","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/gpu-overview"},"next":{"title":"GPU 性能瓶颈分析","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/performance-bottleneck"}},{"id":"03-gpu-basics/performance-bottleneck","title":"GPU 性能瓶颈分析","description":"理解 compute-bound vs memory-bound 是推理优化的核心能力，决定了你该优化计算还是优化带宽。","source":"@site/docs/03-gpu-basics/performance-bottleneck.md","sourceDirName":"03-gpu-basics","slug":"/03-gpu-basics/performance-bottleneck","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/performance-bottleneck","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":3,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":3},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"GPU 显存模型","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/memory-model"},"next":{"title":"GPU 互联与多卡通信","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/gpu-interconnect"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/engine-overview","title":"推理引擎概览","description":"一句话概括：推理引擎是大模型生产部署的核心基础设施，负责把训练好的权重转化为高吞吐、低延迟的在线服务。","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/engine-overview.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/engine-overview","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/engine-overview","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":1,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":1},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"GPU 互联与多卡通信","permalink":"/03-gpu-basics/gpu-interconnect"},"next":{"title":"vLLM 深度解析","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/vllm-deep-dive"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/kv-cache-quant","title":"KV Cache 量化","description":"KV Cache 占据推理显存的 60-80%，量化 KV Cache 是提升吞吐和并发量的最有效手段之一","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/kv-cache-quant.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/kv-cache-quant","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/kv-cache-quant","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":3,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":3},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"量化方案详解","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-schemes"},"next":{"title":"分布式推理概述","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/distributed-overview"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/quantization-basics","title":"模型量化基础","description":"用低精度表示高精度数值，在可控精度损失下将显存压缩 2-4 倍、推理速度提升 1.5-3 倍","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/quantization-basics.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-basics","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-basics","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":1,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":1},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"SGLang 深度解析","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/sglang-deep-dive"},"next":{"title":"量化方案详解","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-schemes"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/quantization-schemes","title":"量化方案详解","description":"深入 AWQ、GPTQ、SmoothQuant、FP8 四大主流方案的原理、对比和选型策略","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/quantization-schemes.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-schemes","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-schemes","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":2,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":2},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"模型量化基础","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-basics"},"next":{"title":"KV Cache 量化","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/kv-cache-quant"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/sglang-deep-dive","title":"SGLang 深度解析","description":"一句话概括：SGLang 是面向 Agent 和结构化生成场景的推理引擎，其核心创新 RadixAttention 通过前缀树管理 KV Cache，配合 FSM 约束生成，在 Agent 工作流中可实现 2-5x 的性能提升。","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/sglang-deep-dive.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/sglang-deep-dive","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/sglang-deep-dive","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":4,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":4},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"TensorRT-LLM 深度解析","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/trt-llm-deep-dive"},"next":{"title":"模型量化基础","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/quantization-basics"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/trt-llm-deep-dive","title":"TensorRT-LLM 深度解析","description":"一句话概括：TensorRT-LLM 是 NVIDIA 官方的 LLM 推理加速库，通过编译时深度优化（kernel fusion、precision calibration）在 NVIDIA GPU 上提供业界最高的推理性能。","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/trt-llm-deep-dive.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/trt-llm-deep-dive","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/trt-llm-deep-dive","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":3,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":3},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"vLLM 深度解析","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/vllm-deep-dive"},"next":{"title":"SGLang 深度解析","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/sglang-deep-dive"}},{"id":"04-inference-optimization/vllm-deep-dive","title":"vLLM 深度解析","description":"一句话概括：vLLM 是目前生态最成熟、使用最广泛的开源 LLM 推理引擎，其核心创新 PagedAttention 将显存利用率从 ~60% 提升到 ~95%。","source":"@site/docs/04-inference-optimization/vllm-deep-dive.md","sourceDirName":"04-inference-optimization","slug":"/04-inference-optimization/vllm-deep-dive","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/vllm-deep-dive","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":2,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":2},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"推理引擎概览","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/engine-overview"},"next":{"title":"TensorRT-LLM 深度解析","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/trt-llm-deep-dive"}},{"id":"05-distributed-inference/distributed-overview","title":"分布式推理概述","description":"一句话概括核心：当单块 GPU 的显存放不下模型、算力撑不住吞吐时，必须通过并行策略把计算和存储切分到多块 GPU 上协同完成。","source":"@site/docs/05-distributed-inference/distributed-overview.md","sourceDirName":"05-distributed-inference","slug":"/05-distributed-inference/distributed-overview","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/distributed-overview","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":1,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":1},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"KV Cache 量化","permalink":"/04-inference-optimization/kv-cache-quant"},"next":{"title":"张量并行（TP）","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/tensor-parallel"}},{"id":"05-distributed-inference/moe-parallel","title":"MoE 并行","description":"一句话概括核心：Mix-of-Experts 通过路由机制让每个 token 只激活部分 Expert，结合 Expert Parallel 将不同 Expert 分布到不同 GPU，实现\"模型越大、激活越少\"的高效推理。","source":"@site/docs/05-distributed-inference/moe-parallel.md","sourceDirName":"05-distributed-inference","slug":"/05-distributed-inference/moe-parallel","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/moe-parallel","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":4,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":4},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"流水线并行（PP）","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/pipeline-parallel"},"next":{"title":"部署架构设计","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/deployment-architecture"}},{"id":"05-distributed-inference/pipeline-parallel","title":"流水线并行（PP）","description":"一句话概括核心：将 Transformer 的不同层分配到不同 GPU，通过 micro-batch 填充计算间隙，让多卡像流水线一样协同处理请求。","source":"@site/docs/05-distributed-inference/pipeline-parallel.md","sourceDirName":"05-distributed-inference","slug":"/05-distributed-inference/pipeline-parallel","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/pipeline-parallel","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":3,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":3},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"张量并行（TP）","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/tensor-parallel"},"next":{"title":"MoE 并行","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/moe-parallel"}},{"id":"05-distributed-inference/tensor-parallel","title":"张量并行（TP）","description":"一句话概括核心：将 Transformer 每层的权重矩阵按行或按列切分到多块 GPU，每层计算完成后通过 AllReduce 同步结果，实现单层级别的细粒度并行。","source":"@site/docs/05-distributed-inference/tensor-parallel.md","sourceDirName":"05-distributed-inference","slug":"/05-distributed-inference/tensor-parallel","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/tensor-parallel","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":2,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":2},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"分布式推理概述","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/distributed-overview"},"next":{"title":"流水线并行（PP）","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/pipeline-parallel"}},{"id":"06-production-deployment/autoscaling","title":"弹性扩缩容","description":"LLM 推理服务的扩缩容不是简单的 \"CPU 高了就加 Pod\"，而是需要感知 GPU 显存、队列深度和模型加载时间的智能调度。","source":"@site/docs/06-production-deployment/autoscaling.md","sourceDirName":"06-production-deployment","slug":"/06-production-deployment/autoscaling","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/autoscaling","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":2,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":2},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"部署架构设计","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/deployment-architecture"},"next":{"title":"可观测性体系","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/observability"}},{"id":"06-production-deployment/deployment-architecture","title":"部署架构设计","description":"生产级 LLM 部署需要完整的组件选型、K8s 编排、GPU 调度和模型生命周期管理，远不止 \"启动一个 Docker 容器\"。","source":"@site/docs/06-production-deployment/deployment-architecture.md","sourceDirName":"06-production-deployment","slug":"/06-production-deployment/deployment-architecture","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/deployment-architecture","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":1,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":1},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"MoE 并行","permalink":"/05-distributed-inference/moe-parallel"},"next":{"title":"弹性扩缩容","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/autoscaling"}},{"id":"06-production-deployment/disaster-recovery","title":"容灾与降级","description":"LLM 推理服务的容灾不只是\"备用服务器\"，还涉及 GPU 硬件故障、模型权重损坏、显存泄漏等特有风险，需要分层次的防御体系。","source":"@site/docs/06-production-deployment/disaster-recovery.md","sourceDirName":"06-production-deployment","slug":"/06-production-deployment/disaster-recovery","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/disaster-recovery","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":4,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":4},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"可观测性体系","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/observability"},"next":{"title":"多租户与平台化","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/multi-tenant"}},{"id":"06-production-deployment/multi-tenant","title":"多租户与平台化","description":"多租户是 LLM 推理平台化的核心挑战：如何在有限的 GPU 上安全、公平、可计量地服务多个业务方，是 FDE 面试中的高频场景。","source":"@site/docs/06-production-deployment/multi-tenant.md","sourceDirName":"06-production-deployment","slug":"/06-production-deployment/multi-tenant","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/multi-tenant","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":5,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":5},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"容灾与降级","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/disaster-recovery"},"next":{"title":"实战实验","permalink":"/12-labs/"}},{"id":"06-production-deployment/observability","title":"可观测性体系","description":"没有可观测性的 LLM 服务就像在黑暗中开飞机，你不知道什么时候会坠毁。LLM 推理的可观测性需要覆盖 GPU 硬件、推理引擎、业务指标三个层次。","source":"@site/docs/06-production-deployment/observability.md","sourceDirName":"06-production-deployment","slug":"/06-production-deployment/observability","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/observability","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":3,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":3},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"弹性扩缩容","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/autoscaling"},"next":{"title":"容灾与降级","permalink":"/06-production-deployment/disaster-recovery"}},{"id":"07-agent-architecture/index","title":"Agent 系统与架构","description":"FDE 需要支持 Agent 场景：记忆、工具调用、多 Agent 协作","source":"@site/docs/07-agent-architecture/index.md","sourceDirName":"07-agent-architecture","slug":"/07-agent-architecture/","permalink":"/07-agent-architecture/","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":1,"frontMatter":{"sidebar_position":1},"sidebar":"tutorialSidebar","previous":{"title":"自建 vs 云 API","permalink":"/08-cost-operations/self-hosted-vs-cloud"},"next":{"title":"前沿技术概述","permalink":"/09-evaluation-frontier/frontier-overview"}},{"id":"08-cost-operations/capacity-planning","title":"容量规划","description":"根据 QPS 预估、GPU 吞吐建模和 SLA 要求，精确计算需要多少 GPU 以及何时扩容。","source":"@site/docs/08-cost-operations/capacity-planning.md","sourceDirName":"08-cost-operations","slug":"/08-cost-operations/capacity-planning","permalink":"/08-cost-operations/capacity-planning","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],